ABn.doc: Filters transactions by entrypoint called on the target contract.

ABo.doc: Filters transactions by operation status (applied, failed, backtracked, skipped).

ABq.doc: Sorts transactions by specified field. Descending sort mode.

ABr.doc: Maximum number of items to return.

ABt.doc: Comma-separated list of ticker symbols to inject historical prices into response.

ACh.doc: Returns transactions where sender OR target is equal to the specified value.
